<p><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200901/567f9c9c42654d44a6866ac08cfea86c.png" width="1975" height="1034" /></p>
<p>来源：MYKEY，CoinMarketCap，Coin Metrics</p>
<p><span>目前，主要稳定币的市场流通</span><span>市值达到</span>165.56亿美元，<span>与上周相比增长</span>6.01<span>亿美元</span><span>。</span></p>
<p><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200901/c9133e7c06b14de2987111da883a32b2.png" width="1902" height="854" /></p>
<p>来源：MYKEY，Coin Metrics</p>            <div class="lookall-box">
