</div>
<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p><span>过去一周，</span>Tether在Tron上增发了两次，共4.5<span>亿</span>USDT。USDC、PAX、TUSD、HUSD、DAI、GUSD的流通量分别增加8648<span>万、</span>1797<span>万、</span>3001<span>万、</span>124<span>万、</span>1506<span>万、</span>128<span>万，</span>BUSD的流通量减少98<span>万。</span></p>
